Class Admin

java.lang.Object
com.purnendu.quizo.models.Admin
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.os.Parcelable
public class Admin extends Object implements android.os.Parcelable
Represents an administrator entity in the Quizo application, used for authentication and management. This class is designed as a Room Entity for database persistence, with fields for username, email, and password. The email serves as the PrimaryKey. It also implements Parcelable to allow efficient data transfer between Android components.

Key fields include:

  • username: The display name of the administrator.
  • email: The unique email address, serving as the primary identifier.
  • password: The hashed password for authentication.
